description:
From the whole Unqualified team, we want to say thank you to all of our sweet sweet listeners for an absolutely stellar year! We wanted to throw together some of our favorite moments from 2016 to celebrate a great year so enjoy part one of Unqualified's memorable moments with guests that include Jennifer Lawrence, Chris Pratt, Shaq, Chris Evans, Jenny Slate, Aubrey Plaza and many more! We love you and can't wait to see what shenanigans we get into in 2017!

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
